General.Name: Bulten AB
General.Description: Bulten AB (publ), together with its subsidiaries, designs, develops, manufactures, and distributes fasteners and related services and solutions for light vehicles, heavy commercial vehicles, automotive, and other industries in Sweden, Poland, Germany, the United Kingdom, rest of Europe, the United States, China, and internationally. The company was formerly known as FinnvedenBulten AB (publ) and changed its name to Bulten AB (publ) in September 2014. The company was founded in 1873 and is headquartered in Gothenburg, Sweden.
